Read the full review: Nigeria Forex Brokers
 
AvaTrade
Overview
Trading on more than 1,250 different financial products across many marketplaces, user-friendly CFD broker AvaTrade is a wonderful choice for newcomers. 
To provide Nigerian Forex traders with a simple mobile trading experience, AvaTrade has developed the AvaTradeGo app. 
With a commission-free account and a 100 USD (41,000 NGN) minimum deposit, AvaTrade offers some of the lowest spreads in the industry, as low as 0.9 pips on the EUR/USD.
 
