Exness
Overview
Over 200,000 traders make use of the services provided by Exness Group, who may choose from trading on over 100 different currency pairs, a handful of cryptocurrencies, 70+ stock CFDs, indices, and commodities. 
If you are an experienced trader in Nigeria, you may choose to open an ECN account, which will cost you raw spreads and 7 USD in commission fees. Beginner traders in Nigeria, on the other hand, can use the Exness Cent Account to get started in live trading.
 
Pros and Cons



PROS
CONS


