Conclusion
While there is currently no way for brokers to gain a regulatory license in Nigeria through the CBN, Nigerian traders are urged to use forex brokers that have Tier-1 and Tier-2 regulations. The brokers that we provided are 4 of the best global forex brokers available to Nigerians.
